e number of $W$--orbits on imaginary\nroots on a hyperboloid of fixed radius is bounded above by the number of root\nlattice points on the hyperboloid that intersect the closure of the fundamental\nregion for $W$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Jul 2014 11:36:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2015 17:16:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
